(222, 1, '2018-05-05 00:01:09', '2018-05-05 00:01:09', '<h2>Fully Responsive</h2>		\n		<p><em>Responsive</em> web design (RWD) is an approach to web design which makes web pages render well on a variety of devices and window or screen sizes. Recent work also considers the viewer proximity as part of the viewing context as an extension for RWD. Content, design and performance are necessary across all devices ...</p>		\n										<img width=\"882\" height=\"648\" src=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/responsive-web-design.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/responsive-web-design.jpg 882w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/responsive-web-design-300x220.jpg 300w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/responsive-web-design-768x564.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 882px) 100vw, 882px\" />											\n										<img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/seo-wheel-ss-1920-800x450.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/seo-wheel-ss-1920-800x450.png 800w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/seo-wheel-ss-1920-800x450-300x169.png 300w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/seo-wheel-ss-1920-800x450-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" />											\n			<h2>SEO Friendly</h2>		\n		<p><b>\"SEO\"</b> refers to <b>search engine optimization</b>, or the process of optimizing a website so that people can easily find it via search engines like Google. By “content,” we mean any information that lives on the web and can be consumed on the web (more on the various types of content below).</p>		\n			<h2>Easy Customization</h2>		\n		<p><em>Customization</em> may refer to: <em>Customization</em> (anthropology), the process of cultural appropriation; Mass<em>customization</em>, the use of computer-aided manufacturing systems to produce <em>custom</em> output; Modding, a slang expression for modification of hardware, software, or other items; Car tuning, the modification of an automobile, ...</p>		\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"754\" src=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/easy-customization-1024x754.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/easy-customization-1024x754.png 1024w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/easy-customization-300x221.png 300w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/easy-customization-768x566.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Documentation-1030x686-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Documentation-1030x686-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Documentation-1030x686-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Documentation-1030x686-768x512.jpg 768w, http://localhost/tqnyah/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Documentation-1030x686.jpg 1030w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>Well Documentation</h2>		\n		<p><em>Documentation</em> is a set of documents provided on paper, or online, or on digital or analog media, such as audio tape or CDs. Examples are user guides, white papers, on-line help, quick-reference guides. It is becoming less common to see paper (hard-copy) <em>documentation</em>. <em>Documentation</em> is distributed via websites, ...</p>', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-05 00:01:09', '2018-05-05 00:01:09', '', 12, 'http://localhost/tqnyah/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
